 <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Soutien aux devoirs</title>

<style>
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef2ff, #ffffff);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 100vh;
}

.container {
    width: 92%;
    max-width: 500px;
    background: white;
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    text-align: center;
}

h1 {
    margin-bottom: 5px;
}

.subtitle {
    color: #555;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.card {
    background: #f7f9ff;
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-top: 15px;
}

.number {
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin: 10px 0;
}

button {
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 8px;
}

.copy {
    background: #333;
    color: white;
}

.whatsapp {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #25D366;
    color: white;
    padding: 12px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.whatsapp:hover {
    background: #1ebe5d;
}

.qr {
    margin-top: 10px;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>📚 Soutien aux devoirs</h1>
<p class="subtitle">
Aide scolaire personnalisée 📖  
Ton soutien me permet de continuer mes études ❤️
</p>

<!-- WAVE -->
<div class="card">
<h3>💰 Soutenir via Wave</h3>

<p class="number" id="waveNumber">+225 01 73 19 70 57</p>

<button class="copy" onclick="copyWave()">📋 Copier le numéro Wave</button>

<div class="qr">
<img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=150x150&data=2250173197057" />
</div>
</div>

<!-- WHATSAPP -->
<div class="card">
<h3>📲 Contact WhatsApp</h3>

<p class="number">+225 05 01 38 87 60</p>

<a class="whatsapp" href="https://wa.me/2250501388760" target="_blank">
💬 Me contacter sur WhatsApp
</a>

<div class="qr">
<img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=150x150&data=https://wa.me/2250501388760" />
</div>
</div>

<!-- NOUVELLES SECTIONS -->
<h2>🎯 Objectif</h2>
<p>Soutenir mes études et financer mon matériel scolaire afin de continuer à apprendre dans de bonnes conditions.</p>

